<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ạsm yswʿ qd ḥlạ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1-ạis̊mu yasūʿa qad̊ ḥalạ
 limas̊maʿi ạl̊mū̊̉min̊
 yasẖ̊fī jirāḥa ạl̊mub̊talay̱
 wāl̊kẖaẘfa yas̊tā̊̉min̊

[V2]
 2- sal̊way̱ ạl̊qulūbi ạl̊kẖāsẖiʿah̊
 taʿ̊zīaẗu ạlạảḥ̊zān̊
 qūtu ạlnũfūsi ạl̊jāyỉʿah̊
 wamaẘridu ạlẓãm̊ận̊

[V3]
 3- wah̊wa ạlãdẖī yusakĩnu
 kẖaẘfī wāảḥ̊zānī
 wadẖik̊ruhu yus̊taḥ̊sanu
 fī sam̊ʿi ậdẖānī

[V4]
 4- bihi ṣalạtī tus̊maʿu
 watugẖ̊faru ạlậtẖām̊
 yakẖ̊zay̱ ạl̊ʿiday̱ ại̹dẖ̊ ạảjidu
 min̊hu ạl̊qabūla ạltãạm̃̊

[V5]
 5- qal̊bī ḍaʿīfuⁿ yā muʿīn̊
 fī ạlsũb̊ḥi qāṣiru
 mā dum̊tu fī wādī ạlạảnīn̊
 fālḍãʿ̊fu ẓāhiru

[V6]
 6- matay̱ ạủsẖāhid̊ka kamā
 ạản̊ta fī baẙti ạlậb̊
 ạủh̊di ạltẖãnā muqadĩmaⁿạ
 sub̊ḥaⁿạ kamā wajab̊</lyrics>
<author>nạṣyf ạlyạzjy, ạlksndr rbnạjl</author>
</song>